_ _7"></span><span class="ls43">《阿弥陀经》<span class="_ _7"></span><span class="ls31">，就认为已经通达了</span></span></span></span></span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y13b ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">佛教。<span class="_ _6"></span>实际上若想深入佛法大海，<span class="_ _6"></span>探寻真理的宝藏，<span class="_ _6"></span>必须要</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y13c ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">了解佛陀第一转法轮、<span class="_ _6"></span>第二转法轮、<span class="_ _6"></span>第三转法轮的教义，<span class="_ _6"></span>包</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y13d ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">括密续也要研究一下。<span class="_ _6"></span>除此之外，<span class="_ _9"></span>印度、<span class="_ _6"></span>藏地、<span class="_ _9"></span>汉地有那么</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y318 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">多高僧大德，<span class="_ _6"></span>他们的传记及其论典，<span class="_ _6"></span>也需要好好拜读。<span class="_ _6"></span>且不</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y319 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">说别的，<span class="_ _6"></span>单单是汉地的<span class="_ _9"></span>《唐高僧传》<span class="_ _7"></span>、<span class="_ _c"></span>《宋高僧传》<span class="_ _7"></span>、<span class="_ _c"></span>《新续高</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y31a ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls36 ws0">僧传》<span class="_ _7"></span><span class="ls15">，看了以后也会让你觉得，<span class="ls10">修行人战胜烦恼、获得快</span></span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y31b ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">乐的境界，实在无法用语言来描述。 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
